<h1>Soul Abrasion and Spell Casting Fury</h1>
	<B>Vorth_TMS wrote: <BR><BR>It was stated shortly after the release of Luclin that it was a bug that Soul Abrasion and Spell Casting Fury were not stacking with Shourd of Death. Is this being looked at? <BR><BR>Here is the information. If you have Spell Casting Fury any level, and do NOT have Soul Abrassion, Shroud of Death will critical for extra damage on occasion. This is very nice and all Shadow Knights like this. However once you train 1 point into Soul Abrassion, Shroud of Death will no longer critical. <BR><BR>Could you please provide the current status of this?</B> <BR><BR><BR>I sure can. <BR><BR>We've changed the way these two abilities work. After the next patch Spell Casting Fury will be checked first. If it fails and there is no critical, then Soul Abrasion will take effect. They won't stack, and they really shouldn't, but one or the other will work. <BR><BR>Alan


